inn1.comm: And he starts off with a wayward delivery outside the off stump - bit of nerves?

Nerves? what nerves! good length delivery, pitched in line with the off stump and this one swung back in sharply - too good a delivery for Powell who is beaten comprehensively and the ball thuds in to the pad and that's plumb.
good length delivery outside the off stump, Smith pushes forward and defends it away towards covers
Alam is talking! good length and this one swung as well, Smith pokes at it and is beaten by a long way
bit wide outside the off stump and this one went straight on - Powell leaves it through to the keeper
fuller length delivery and that's punched down to mid-off. Straight to the fielder and there is no room for a single there
in the slot outside the off stump and Powell drives hard towards cover. Shakib there dives across to his left and cuts off a certain boundary. End of a fine first over from Alam

top delivery first up, pitched in line with the off stump and this one shaped back in to the right-hander. Fletcher looks to defend on the back-foot and is hit on the pad. Loud appeal for lbw turned down - probably missing leg
beaten outside the off stump - still just the one slip in place
fuller length delivery on the pads and Fletcher clips it down to fine leg for a single
shot! bit of width offered outside the off stump. Smith goes back and across and slices it away to the backward point fence. Was hit hard and the fielder at third man had no chance of cutting it off
driven away off the back-foot to the cover region
pitched up in the channel outside the off stump, Smith gets forward and defends it down on the off side
good length delivery on the middle and off stump line, hint of away swing and Fletcher is made to defend
slower delivery on the middle and leg stump line, Fletcher looks to defend it down on the leg side, ball clips the outer half of the bat and rolls away towards point
again good length and on the middle and off stump line, Fletcher gets right behind this one and defends it with a straight bat
fuller in length, again swinging away a touch - Fletcher gets forward and drives it straight to the fielder at cover
another line and length delivery, defended watchfully

take that! good length delivery, pitched close to the off stump line and swinging away a touch. Fletcher gets well forward and hammers it straight back past the bowler and well wide of the fielder at mid-off
cleaned up! good length and swinging in a touch. Smith has a mighty swing at it with his eyes closed. Misses the target by miles and the ball crashes into the stumps
down the leg side
good length delivery outside the off stump, defended watchfully
fuller length delivery outside the off stump, Dowlin gets forward and defends it with a straight bat
short of a good length and this one nipped back in, Dowlin gets right on top of the bounce and plays it down
pitched up wide outside the off stump, Dowlin stretches forward and drives, looking to get it away through covers but the ball clips the outside edge and races away to third man
pitched up on the pads and Fletcher flicks it away to the vacant third man fence -  easy pickings
defended outside the off stump, ball rolls down to silly mid-on
pushed away towards cover point and they scamper through for a single, throw at the bowler's end misses the target and Dowlin makes it across safely. Direct hit would have been fatal
short of a good length delivery outside the off stump, Fletcher stands tall and defends it down on the off side
pitched up and drifting down the leg side
MAX! pitched up outside the off stump, Fletcher steps forward, gets to the pitch of the delivery and lofts it over the long-off fence. Hit right through the line and the ball just sailed away
cut away well in front of point, straight to the fielder though

going...going...gone! another pitched up delivery, this time bit straighter and Fletcher dismisses it over the long-on fence. Another clean hit through the line -  this is exciting cricket from Fletcher
good length delivery outside the off stump, defended watchfully
good length delivery outside the off stump, width offered and Dowlin goes after it but fails to make contact
slower delivery outside the off stump, Dowlin waits for it and cuts it away straight to the fielder at point
good length delivery outside the off stump, defended
slower delivery gone wrong - ends up as a low fulltoss on the pads and Dowlin clips it away to the backward square leg fence
slightly short, pitched outside the off stump and coming in with the angle - Dowlin stays back, gets behind the line and defends it with a straight bat
good length delivery, close to the off stump line and Fletcher taps it away on the off side
defended away towards mid-off again a defensive shot
on the middle and leg stump line, full in length. Fletcher just lines it up and drives it through the gap between mid-on and midwicket. Lovely shot
slightly short and outside the off stump, defended standing tall on the back-foot
on the middle and leg stump line, Fletcher moves across and clips it away to the fine leg fence, was on one foot as he made contact, bit of old Caribbean flavor in that shot
four more, again forced away on one foot - was on the pads and he got it past the fielder at midwicket
turned away on the leg side and they scamper through for a single, bit of hesitation going for the single but the throw from the fielder hits Dowlin on the stretch
defended off the back-foot
taps it away on the off side
forced away off the back-foot to the cover region
punched off the back-foot and straight to the fielder at point
down the leg side
quicker delivery to end the over - Fletcher stands tall on the back-foot and defends it down on the off side
full and on the stumps, Dowlin steps forward and drives it straight to the fielder at midwicket
flat delivery on the middle and off stump line, defended stretching well forward
this one nipped in with the arm, Dowlin goes back to cut and is almost beaten, gets an outside edge and the ball rolls away behind the stumps
defended down on the leg side
another straight delivery, Fletcher plays across the line and gets hit on the pad, that looked close but umpire Duncin was not interested
wide delivery outside the off stump, swing and a miss from Fletcher
short ball outside the off stump, Dowlin cuts and the ball rolls away off the edge
defended stretching well forward, bat and pad held together
swipe across the line makes perfect contact and the ball races away to the midwicket fence
slightly short and close to the off stump line, Dowlin goes back and cuts late, again makes perfect contact and the ball races away to the third man fence
jumble of bat and pad, loud appeal for lbw turned down
cut away hard but straight to the fielder at point
on the middle stump. Dowlin gets behind the line of the delivery and defends it back onto the pitch
upto the batsman on the off stump. Dowlin comes forward and defends
on the off stump. Dowlin gets onto the front foot and defends
on the middle stump and pushes it to mid-on
outside off. Dowlin opens the face of the bat as he pushes it to point
short on the middle stump. Dowlin gets behind the line and plays it down with soft hands
width outside the off stump. Fletcher rocks back and punishes it through extra-cover for a boundary
outside off and short in length. Fletcher defends it off the back foot
wide down the leg side and the batsman run a single as the ball is deflected off Rahim's gloves
wide down the leg side again
arm-ball on the off and middle. Dowlin comes forward and defends
straight delivery outside the off stump and left alone by Dowlin
off the outside edge from the off stump for a boundary. Slip would have easily taken the catch had he been present
slogs to midwicket from off stump
gets behind the line outside off and defends
outside off. Comes forward and pushes it back to the bowler
on the middle stump. Fletcher pushes it to leg side
outside off. Fletcher gets an outside edge to gully
outside off and fuller in length. Fletcher drives it to extra-cover and Shakib has two maidens on a trot
outside off and Dowlin defends off the back foot
on the leg stump. Dowlin forces it off the back foot to square leg for a single
full on the middle. Fletcher sweeps it away to deep square leg for a boundary
fuller on the off stump. Fletcher hoicks it across the line as he deposits the ball over long-on for a six
outside off. Fletcher comes forward and defends
fuller on the middle and leg. Fletcher slogs it across the line, just evading the midwicket fielder for a boundary and he gets to his half-century with that shot
outside off. Turns it to midwicket
forces it to cover off the back foot
on the leg stump. Dowlin turns it to short fine-leg for a single
on the leg stump again as Fletcher pushes it to square-leg for a single
on the off stump. Dowlin drives it to extra-cover
drives it to cover to a ball pitched outside the off stump

and Fletcher goes! He gets a fuller delivery on the middle and leg. He attempts the same shot with which he got a six of the last Razzak over but finds Ashraful on the fence as the Powerplay restrictions are off and he has to return back to the pavilion
flat delivery outside the off stump, defended stretching well forward
padded away from well outside the off stump
driven straight back, Razzak fails to stop it cleanly and the ball rolls down to mid-on
bowled from round the stumps and this one goes on to hit Dowlin on the pad, appeal for lbw turned down
forced away off the front-foot and the ball rolls away behind the stumps on the off side. End of a successful over
width offered outside the off stump, cut away straight to the fielder at point
tossed up outside the off stump, defended stretching well forward
quicker delivery outside the off stump, defended on the front-foot. Not a convincing shot
wide delivery outside the off stump, was there to be hit but Reifer leaves it through to the keeper
stretches forward to defend and gets hit on the pad, appeal turned down
another wide delivery outside the off stump, no shot offered
driven off the back-foot and past the diving fielder at short cover, easy single
defended outside the off stump and the ball rolls away behind the stumps
fuller length delivery outside the off stump, Reifer gets forward and drives it straight back to the bowler
turned away straight to the fielder at short midwicket
drifting down the leg side, Reifer goes down on one knee and looks to sweep but fails to make contact, ball clips the pad and runs down to fine leg
worked away on the leg side for an easy single
pitched outside the leg stump and drifting down further - Rahim does well to collect it cleanly
driven down to long-on for a single
gets a good stride across and shoulders arms
pitched outside the off stump and turning away, Reifer covers his stumps and leaves it through to the keeper
defended outside the off stump
punched down the track, watchfully played
in the channel outside the off stump, Reifer once again gets well forward and plays it away towards cover
worked away with the turn to the midwicket region
pitched outside the off stump and turning in, Reifer goes back and punches it down to mid-on - straight to the fielder there
forced away off the back-foot and the ball rolls away behind the stumps on the leg side
drifting down the leg side and Reifer taps it down to fine leg for a single
swept away to deep fine leg, again just the single
pushes forward and turns it away towards midwicket, another quiet overs goes by
turned away off the back-foot to the midwicket region, fielder moves across quickly and cuts of the single
again worked away on the leg side, this time straight to the fielder at short midwicket
nicely turned away to deep midwicket
pitched close to the off stump line and turning in, Reifer goes back and looks to turn it away but fails to make contact. Loud appeal for lbw turned down - that looked out
defended outside the off stump
hit hard into the ground on the off side and the ball bounces over the fielder at short cover
good length delivery outside the off stump, defended watchfully

short of a good length delivery outside the off stump, no width on offer there but Reifer cuts hard, ball clips the top edge and races away to the third man fence. The fielder in the deep had no chance of cutting it off
good length delivery outside the off stump, Reifer stands tall on the back-foot and punches it past the fielder at short cover
good length delivery outside the off stump, defended
turned away off the back-foot to the midwicket region
pitched up down the leg side and Dowlin whips it away fine to the fence
punched down to mid-on
tries to work it away on the leg side but fails to make contact
pushes it to long-off for a single
outside off. Comes forward and drives it to long-off for a single
outside the off stump. Looks to sweep it away and is beaten
outside the off stump. Reifer comes forward and pushes it to cover
short on the middle stump. Dowlin gets onto the back foot and pushes it to long-on for a single
outside the leg stump. Off the pads to short fine-leg
short outside the off stump. Reifer looks to cut it away and is beaten
short outside off. Reifer cuts it to point
on the middle stump. Reifer clips it to midwicket
fuller outside the off stump. Reifer pushes it to cover
on the leg stump. Dowlin turns it away to fine-leg for a couple, first of the innings
on the leg stump. Dowlin comes forward and pushes it to midwicket
comes down the track to a flighted delivery on the leg stump to push it to long-on for a single
comes down the track to a delivery on the leg stump and clips it to deep midwicket for a single
wide down the leg side
pushes it to midwicket for a single

and that is what happens when you don't rotate the strike! Reifer pushes it to short fine-leg and wants a single. Dowlin runs across and can't beat the throw by Ashraful and at half-way stage West Indies find themselves four down
on the leg stump. Reifer comes down the track and clips it away to deep midwicket for a couple
spears it into the middle stump as Reifer defends it back on the pitch
outside the off stump. Reifer pushes it back to the bowler
off the outside edge to point
on the leg stump. Reifer comes down the track and forces it past midwicket for a boundary
on the off stump. Reifer looks to clip it away on the leg side and gets a leading edge to off side for a single
on the leg stump. Reifer pushes it to midwicket for a single
fuller on the off stump. Bernard comes forward and pushes it to the cover fielder
arm-ball on the leg stump. Bernard pads it away
outside the off stump. Bernard defends it on the off-side
on the leg stump. Bernard turns it away to short fine-leg for a single
on the leg stump. Reifer turns it to short fine-leg
and Bernard goes exactly the same way as Fletcher went as he holes out to long-on where Ashraful takes an easy catch. West Indies in serious trouble now
flat delivery outside the off stump, defended off the back-foot
driven down to long-on, Sammy gets off the mark with an easy single
pitched up outside the off stump and that's driven straight back to the bowler
flat delivery outside the off stump, Reifer gets well forward and defends it with bat and pad held together
pushed away on the leg side, Reifer is really struggling to get the spinners away
full and on the off stump line, driven straight back to the bowler
defended stretching well forward
gets inside the line of this one and drives down to long-off for a single, well played
finally Reifer gets hold of one - comes down the track to the pitch of the delivery and lofts it over the wide long-on fence. Good clean hit
again comes down the track and drives it down to long-on
punched off the back-foot and the ball rolls back to the bowler
worked away off the back-foot to the midwicket region
defended outside the off stump, bat and pad held together
comes down the track and drives it away to deep midwicket
full and straight, driven with a straight bat to long-on
slightly short, Reifer goes back and cuts it away straight to the fielder at short third man
comes down the track to the pitch of the delivery and drives it down to long-on
pushes forward to defend, bat and pad held together
quicker delivery, Reifer gets well forward and taps it away on the off side, not a convincing shot
worked away towards midwicket
driven down to long-on, solid shot
worked away nicely to deep midwicket, easy single added to the total
width offered outside the off stump, Reifer cuts well but finds the fielder at backward point
driven straight back bowler, hit hard but the placement was wrong
edged away to cover
fuller length delivery, again driven back to the bowler
comes down the track and looks to work it away on the leg side but fails to make contact
drifting down the leg side, Sammy looks to play it fine but makes no contact and the ball rolls away off the pad
in the slot and Sammy hits this right back over the bowler's head for a boundary, clean hit
comes down the track and lofts him away to deep midwicket for a couple
on the leg stump, sweeps it to square leg for a single
forces it to square leg
on the off stump. Sammy lofts it to long-on for a boundary
outside the off stump. Sammy gets a boundary again by forcing the ball past the point fielder
retains the strike by pushing a delivery pitched on the leg stump to long-on
fuller on the off stump. Sammy moves across and lofts it high over the sight screen for a six
and this time he slogs it away to midwicket for a six
wide down the leg side and batsmen change ends as Rahim fumbles with the take
outside the off stump. Reifer comes forward and defends
fuller outside the off stump. Reifer pushes it to the cover fielder
fuller on the middle stump as Reifer plays it back to the bowler
off the outside edge to short third-man for a single
on the leg stump as Reifer comes down the track and turns it away to deep backward square leg for a single
outside off. Comes forward and defends it to cover
short outside the off stump. Reifer pulls it with power to deep midwicket for a boundary
on the leg stump. Clips it to deep square leg for a single
defends it back to the bowler
on the leg stump. Sammy lofts it by getting inside the line to long-on for a boundary
turns it to short fine-leg
on the middle stump, defends it back to the bowler
on the leg stump. Forces it to midwicket
pushes to point and runs across for a quick single
on the middle stump. Sammy defends it back to the bowler
on the leg stump. Sammy turns it away to midwicket for a single
short outside the off stump. Sammy looks to cut it away with no feet movement and is beaten
wide outside the off stump and it's a poor delivery
fuller and closer to the stumps this time. Sammy looks to guide it away and is beaten
full-toss outside the off stump. Sammy comes forward and places it over extra-cover for a boundary
dropped as Alam pitches it short and Sammy cuts it. The fielder at cover dives and does not get his hands around it
fuller on the middle stump. Reifer plays it back to the bowler
fuller on the middle and leg. Reifer comes forward and clips it to midwicket where Shakib does no mistake and takes the catch. Reifer had a torturous stay at the wicket
outside the off stump. Sammy comes forward and pushes it to cover
outside the off stump. Sammy comes forward and pushes it back to the bowler
comes forward and pushes it to long-on for a single
outside the off stump. Thomas pushes it to deep point and gets a single
outside the off stump and left alone by Sammy
Razzak gets a gift as he bowls a full delivery by giving it a little more air as Sammy spoons it back to him and Razzak fumbles and takes it on the second attempt
outside the off stump and coming in. Thomas lets it go to the keeper
wide down the leg side
outside the off stump. Cut to point off the back foot
on the middle stump. Thomas pushes it to long-on and takes a sharp single. Tamim's throw does not find the target
down the leg side but brushes the thigh pad and up goes Rahim in appeal
width outside the off stump. Miller cuts it away to deep point for a single
wide down the leg side. Rahim does well to dive across and take the ball
outside the off stump. Thomas opens the face of the bat and gets a single to third-man
down the leg side, wasted delivery
punched off the back-foot to the cover region, diving stop saves runs but fails to cut off the single
another wayward delivery down the leg side - 16 wides so far in this innings!
driven away straight to the fielder at short midwicket
tossed up outside the off stump and that's driven in the air to the cover fence, clean hit from Miller
full and drifting in, Miller fails to make contact and the ball zips past the off side, close call
worked away towards square leg, quick single taken
comes forward and drives it down to long-on
pitched up on the middle and off stump line, Thomas pushes forward and drives it straight to the fielder at mid-on
fulltoss on the stumps and Thomas punches it down to mid-on, takes on the fielder there and Thomas makes it across comfortably
another fulltoss, just outside the off stump and that's driven away to deep cover
slow yorker, Thomas comes forward, defends it away towards cover point and runs hard for the single
good length delivery on the middle and leg stump line, Miller stays back and defends it with a straight bat
short of a good length delivery, close to the off stump line and Miller cuts it straight to the fielder at point
full and on the pads and that's driven wide of the diving fielder at midwicket, runs hard and comes back comfortably for the second
full and on the stumps and Thomas drives it inside out to long-off
full and on the pads and Miller clips it away to deep backward square leg
cut away from right in front of the stumps to the backward point region
Thomas! slightly short and close to the off stump line, Thomas waits for the ball on the back-foot and at the last moment dabs it past the fielder at short third man
played away off the back-foot, this time the ball goes straight to the fielder at short third man
on the middle and off stump line, defended with a straight bat
drifting on to the pads and Miller works it away towards the vacant square leg
comes down the track and lofts it away to deep midwicket, fielder in the deep moves across quickly but fails to get there in time, does well to cut off the boundary though
turned away on the leg side for an easy single
gone this time! Miller once again comes down the track and lofts the ball to deep square leg, this time Mahmudullah moves across quickly and takes a good low catch. West Indies 9 down
hit away towards midwicket, not a well timed shot
slightly short and angled into the right hander, defended off the back-foot
defended outside the off stump
looks to work it away on the leg side and the ball rolls away off the outside edge to the short third man region
on the middle and off stump line, defended watchfully and the ball rolls back to the bowler
pushed to cover, again no room for a single there
quicker delivery, Roach stays back and defends it down on the leg side
down the leg side
would you believe it, another one down the leg side
defended down on the leg side, no single there
turned away straight to the fielder at short midwicket
dabs it down to short third man, gets it wide of the fielder there and they scamper through for a single
turned away off the pads, gets it just wide of the fielder at square leg and once again they scamper through for a single
drifting down the leg side, Thomas goes back and across and clips it down to fine leg where Razzak fails to stop it cleanly
swept away to short fine leg, this time Razzak makes no mistaken - seven runs off the over
on the stumps and Thomas slogs it away to deep midwicket
turned away from well outside the off stump to the vacant square leg region, runs hard for the first run and comfortably comes back for the second
on the middle and off stump line, Roach goes back and turns it away well wide of the fielder at midwicket
comes down the track and Shakib pulls it back a bit, in the end Thomas defends it down on the off side
played away on the leg side, midwicket moves across quickly and cuts off the single
goes for the slog sweep and ends up with a top edge, ball balloons over the keeper and runs down to the boundary
short of a good length delivery, drifting down the leg side and Roach pulls it away to the fine leg fence, easy runs
played away on the leg side and they scamper through for a single
lofted down to long-off, falls just short of the fielder moving in from the deep
short ball, swings across but fails to make contact

stunning catch! Roach hits it into the breeze to the deep midwicket region, Tamim runs in from the deep, drives full length forward and takes it inches away from the ground and manages to hold on to the ball on the forward slide
driven down to long-off and Thomas retains the strike
punched off the back-foot and the ball rolls back to the bowler
turned away off the back-foot and gets it wide of the fielder at mid-on
full and on the pads, Tonge drives it down to long-on

what a mess! Thomas clips one off the pads to deep midwicket, easy two on but Thomas slips while turning for the second. Tonge never looks up and keeps running with Thomas down at the other end, throw comes in at the keeper's end and the bails are removed with Tonge half way down the pitch

inn2.comm: short outside the off stump. Tamim stands tall and cuts it away to third man where Tonge messes up with the fielding and concedes an extra run
outside the off stump. Tamim  lets it go and Roach is lucky to get away without it being called a wide
fuller on the leg stump. Tamim leans forward and clips it away to the right of midwicket fielder for a boundary
and a fast bowlers reply as Tamim is squared by an away going delivery pitching around the off stump
and there goes the ball flying as he provides Tamim with the width and he flays it some power to point for a boundary
spears it onto the legs as Tamim clips it effortlessly through midwicket for a boundary
outside the off stump and left alone
on the leg stump. Junaid flicks it to fine-leg for a single
outside the off stump. Tamim plays it off the back foot to point
on the leg stump and Tamim gets onto the back foot again and turns it away to fine-leg for a single
fuller on the leg stump and it's Junaid's turn to capitalise as he flicks it away to deep backward square leg for a boundary
outside the off stump and short in length. Junaid gets on top of the bounce of the delivery and pushes it to point
short outside the off stump. Tamim it is who gets on top of the delivery and defends it back onto the pitch
timing of Tamim is back as he feasts himself on a fuller delivery on the leg stump. Tamim flicks it to deep midwicket for a boundary
short outside the off stump. Tamim stands tall and cuts it past the point fielder for a superbly timed boundary
comes forward and plays it with soft hands to midwicket for a single
short ball outside the off stump. Junaid stands tall and flays it over cover for a boundary
good length delivery on the leg stump. Tamim stands tall and defends it back to the  bowler
outside the off stump. Tamim comes forward and pushes it to cover
outside off and left alone by Tamim
stands tall and pushes it to point
outside the off stump. Tamim punches it to mid-off
outside the off stump. Junaid comes forward and pushes it to mid-off for a quick single
extra effort by Sammy as he bounces Tamim with a delivery outside the off stump
fuller outside the off stump. Tamim comes forward and drives it to short extra cover for just that shot
outside the off stump. Tamim comes forward in an attempt to defend as he expects no movement. Tamim is beaten by the away movement
outside the off stump. Tamim gets behind the line of the delivery and defends it back to the bowler
and again
short outside the off stump. Junaid gets on top of the bounce again as he opens the face of the bat and pushes it to point
good length delivery on the leg stump. Junaid clips it away effortlessly to the left of mid-on fielder for a boundary
on the leg stump and short in length as Junaid defends it onto the leg side
short outside the off stump. Junaid moves across and pulls it away to deep midwicket for a boundary
pitching on the middle stump and moving away as Junaid looks to steer it away and is beaten
short outside the off stump. Junaid runs it down to third man for a single
short outside the off stump. Junaid pushes it to point
outside the off stump. Junaid moves across and punches it to mid-off
outside the off stump. Junaid plays it with soft hands to third man for a single
short outside the off stump. Tamim moves across and pushes it to point
fuller outside the off stump. Tamim moves across just a touch and lofts it high and handsome over the bowler's head to long-off for a six. Clean hitting that
full-toss on the off stump. Junaid does not pick it as he is playing for the short delivery and adjusts at the last moment to defend it back to the bowler
outside the off stump and moving away. Siddique covers the line of the delivery and lets it go to the keeper
outside the off stump and moving away. Junaid lets this one also go
fuller on the off stump. Junaid moves across and swings through the line as he lofts it to long-on for a boundary
on the leg stump. Junaid defends it to the leg side
slower delivery outside the off stump. Junaid picks it and guides it to short third-man
good length delivery on the off and middle. Tamim gets a huge stride forward and presses the ball back onto the pitch

and finally a wicket falls! Tamim takes his front foot out of the way and swings across the line. He can't keep the ball down as the fielder at mid-on, Powell, leaps and takes the catch easily. Well it is not as easy as it looks
comes forward and defends it to cover
short on the leg stump. Ashraful leaps and plays it late as he defends it back onto the pitch
good length delivery outside the off stump. Ashraful moves across and gets behind the line of the delivery as he defends it
good length delivery outside the off stump. Ashraful comes forward and presents the full face of the bat
fuller outside the off stump. Junaid comes forward and punches it to mid-off
good length delivery outside the off stump. Junaid stands tall and defends it back to the pitch
outside the off stump. Junaid gets onto the back foot and runs it down to third man for a single
wide down the leg side
outside the off stump and moving away. Ashraful moves across and lets it go to the keeper
good length delivery outside the off stump. Ashraful comes forward and defends it back to the bowler
fuller outside the off stump. Ashraful comes forward and drives it to cover
short on the middle and leg. Junaid rocks back and pulls it away to deep square leg for a single
outside the off stump and moving away. Ashraful moves across and lets it go
fuller outside the off stump. Ashraful comes forward and defends it to cover
width outside the off stump. Ashraful flashes and does not get enough bat on the ball as it trickles to sweeper cover and he gets a couple
on the leg stump. Ashraful turns it away to midwicket for a couple
outside the off stump and left alone by Ashraful
outside the off stump and short in length as Junaid runs it down to third man for a single
short outside the off stump. Ashraful guides it in the gap between first slip and the third slip for a boundary
short outside the off stump. Ashraful runs it down to third man for a single
short outside the off stump. Junaid moves across and stands tall as he guides the ball to point
short outside the off stump. Junaid moves it across and looks to flay it through covers but does not get enough bat on it
on the leg stump. Junaid stands tall and pushes it to the leg side
full outside the off stump. Ashraful comes forward and punches it back to the bowler
short length delivery outside the off stump. Ashraful moves across and drives it to cover
short on the middle and leg. Ashraful gets onto the back foot and pulls it away to deep midwicket for a boundary. Superb shot that
outside off and Ashraful defends
short outside the off stump. Ashraful looks to cut it away and gets a bottom edge to point
short delivery outside the off stump. Ashraful gets behind the line of the delivery and defends
fuller outside the off stump. Junaid moves across and steers it away to third man for a single
wide down the leg side
outside the off stump. Ashraful cuts it away to third man for a single
